728035f-a.text:
Springfield Boulevard, west side, (about 200 feet back from Road) opposite 115th Road, (nearly opposite the N. Kromenacker house of 1891), showing the J.M. Highby house of 1873. Other owners were Jos. J. Hendrickson 1891, and S. Kromenacker in 1907.

April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
